{
  "stem": "11144.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My older niece got married, and she wanted very badly to go to the wedding, because she loved that girl.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She loved her above everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she went-- she went to the wedding, and she stayed in Poland for vacation, really, after the wedding, when all of a sudden, I got the telephone that she had developed a detached retina.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So within two weeks, we brought her back here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She went through a couple of operations here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was with me at that time for a few years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe two years or three years we were living here together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then my younger niece was getting married, and she wanted very badly to go to that wedding again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she wanted me to go, and now I feel very guilty I didn't go with her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow at that time, I just-- Poland was not a country that I really was cherishing, and when I went, I went only to see my mother, really.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Really, that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I didn't want to go and when she was saying, Poland, I said, no.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, she did not go to the wedding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after the wedding, three years ago-- well, two and a half years ago in the summer-- her friend from Poland came here and she was going back and she says, why don't you come with me, just for a visit?",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and she didn't know whether she was going to liquidate at that time or not, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyhow, she went back with this woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went-- we went to Scandinavia for vacation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I came back, and she was coming back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was with me on the phone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She says, I really feel good here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, she was making suits to order.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
